g.text: Since 2004, ClearCompany has empowered thousands of companies to attract, screen, and hire better talent, engage their team, and use strategic insights to keep their recruiting competitive. From candidate sourcing with 160 million talent profiles, to discounted posting, automated screening, texting, grading and interview scheduling, to easily building talent pools, EEO/OFCCP compliance reporting and much more, ClearCompany gives you everything you need to find, hire and engage.
We serve clients in every industry, ranging in size from just a few dozen employees to tens of thousands.
